==Home release==
On May 30, 2006, [[Lionsgate Home Entertainment]] released both the first nine episodes of ''ALF: The Animated Series'' as ''ALF Animated Adventures&nbsp;&ndash; 20,000 Years in Driving School and Other Stories;'' and the first seven episodes of ''ALF Tales'' entitled ''ALF and The Beanstalk and Other Classic Fairy Tales'' on [[DVD]] in [[DVD region code#1|Region 1]].

Currently, the Complete Series of both shows are available for viewing on [[Hulu Plus]].

