'''The Artists Organization''' was an artist management company whose clients included [[Animal Collective]], [[Avey Tare]], [[Chromeo]], [[The Joy Formidable]],<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thejoyformidable.com/contact-us|title=The Joy Formidable - Contact Us|accessdate=3 October 2013}}</ref> [[The Knocks]], [[Mike Crossey]], [[Panda Bear (musician)]], [[Poketo]], [[Portugal. The Man]],<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.portugaltheman.com/contact-us|title=Portugal. The Man - Contact Us|accessdate=19 June 2013}}</ref> [[Soundgarden]], and [[Tears for Fears]]. It was based out of [[Santa Monica]], [[California|CA]] and [[New York City|New York]], [[New York (state)|NY]] <ref>{{cite web|url=http://taorganization.com|title=The Artists Organization|accessdate=19 June 2013}}</ref>

